> **MCP is like USB-C for AI.**
>
> Before USB-C, every device had a different charger. Annoying! 😤
> USB-C is one standard plug that works everywhere.
>
> MCP is the "USB-C" that lets any AI plug into any tool — cleanly, reliably, and without reinventing the wheel every time. 🔌✨

